gif\" style=\"margin: 3px 6px 0 0;\" />\n<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/discover/categories/technology?ref=NewsJul0512&amp;utm_campaign=Jul05&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=newsletter\" style=\"color:#999999;text-decoration:none;\" target=\"_top\">Technology</a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"location\" style=\"color: #999999;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 11px;font-weight: normal;margin: 0 0 0 0;line-height: 20px;\">\n<img align=\"left\" alt=\"Location\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://d297h9he240fqh.cloudfront.net/cache-79d64d401/images/emails/location.gif\" style=\"margin: 3px 6px 0 0;\" />\n<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/discover/cities/brooklyn-ny?ref=NewsJul0512&amp;utm_campaign=Jul05&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=newsletter\" style=\"color:#999999;text-decoration:none;\" target=\"_top\">Brooklyn, NY</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"excerpt\" style=\"padding: 0 20px;border-left: 1px solid #e5e5e5;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"334\">\n<h2 style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;color: #333333;margin: 0 0 10px;\">One small step</h2>\n<div class=\"blurb\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #666666;margin: 0 0 10px;line-height: 20px;\"><p>With the fledgling commercial space industry making major strides, a fundamental problem for space travel remains in need of a better solution: the space suit. Artist Ted Southern has teamed up with veteran space suit engineer Nikolay Moiseev to develop an inexpensive, lightweight suit capable of providing astronauts with unprecedented mobility.\xC2\xA0Bulky space suits of yore are about to take a giant leap forward.\xC2\xA0</p></div>\n<div class=\"action\">\n<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/872281861/final-frontier-designs-3g-space-suit?ref=NewsJul0512&amp;utm_campaign=Jul05&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=newsletter\" style=\"color: #55A4F2;text-decoration: none;font-family: Helvetica, Arial,